16
00:01:41,994 --> 00:01:43,636
Di mana awak, Cheon Seo Jin?

17
00:01:43,789 --> 00:01:45,596
Dia berada di bilik latihan.

18
00:01:47,491 --> 00:01:49,097
Berani dia keluar tanpa izin saya?

19
00:01:49,122 --> 00:01:51,323
Saya minta kelas peribadi
